metadata.name: #001 -  MechaBengz
metadata.description:
MechaMiniX and Cryptobengz come together in the first-ever Singapore [SG] NFT community collaboration to present two extraordinary NFT Art pieces. A one-of-one collaboration between the insane minds of two NFT brands that are distinct yet fused with an unexpected art piece.

We presentsâ€“ Anti CryptoBengz CryptoBengz Club [ACCC] MechaBengz. We are a club where we are different from the Web2.0 world, thus, born a human with a half bengz and a half mecha identity. A one-of-a-kind artifact influenced profoundly by our local culture and unique core identity. Finally, the fiery aura is a homage to the legendary Aurabengz.

You will own one of the first local NFT art piece collabs that may well be written in your kid's NFT history book in the future.
